://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/630/1577310.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/630/1577310.jpg"},"summary":"<p><b>Unacceptable</b> features Ed Gamble as host with two teams of comics battling to convince a studio audience of their most daft, niche, unwise or unacceptable views that they and their teammates must then defend.</p><p>Joined by some of the biggest names in comedy each week, <i>Unacceptable </i>will see a live \"swingometer\" track how many audience members the teams win over with their wit and punchlines as they aim to convince the crowd, with Gamble introducing a series of challenges to force them to practice what they preach.</p>","updated":1783026124,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/90756"},"nextepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3639173","name":"Episode 1"}}},"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3639173"},"show":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/90756","name":"Unacceptable"}}},{"id":3650900,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3650900/love-island-13x30-episode-30","name":"Episode 30","season":13,"number":30,"type":"regular","airdate":"2026-07-05","airtime":"21:00","airstamp":"2026-07-05T20:00:00+00:00","runtime":65,"rating":{"average":null},"image":null,"summary":null,"show":{"id":11363,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/11363/love-island","name":"Love Island","type":"Reality","language":"English","genres":["Romance"],"status":"Running","runtime":65,"averageRuntime":64,"premiered":"2015-06-07","ended":null,"officialSite":"https://www.itv.com/watch/love-island/2a3697","schedule":{"time":"21:00","days":["Monday","Tuesday","Wednesday","Thursday","Friday","Sunday"]},"rating":{"average":7.2},"weight":98,"network":{"id":54,"name":"ITV2","country":{"name":"United Kingdom","code":"GB","timezone":"Europe/London"},"officialSite":"https://www.itv.com/hub/itv2"},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":null,"thetvdb":296669,"imdb":"tt4770018"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/627/1568469.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/627/1568469.jpg"},"summary":"<p>On <b>Love Island</b> the Islanders must do their best to flirt, date, couple up in a bid to avoid being ‘dumped' from the Island. With new arrivals, heads may turn, while others will prove their true feelings. From romance and heart-to-hearts, to betrayal, bombshells and broken hearts, there's never a dull moment in the ultimate search for love. More texts, fire pit gatherings and challenges await the lovestruck Islanders, meaning there'll be plenty for them to dish the dirt on in the Beach Hut. Twists and turns will follow every step of the way, with shock recouplings, unexpected breakups and dramatic dumpings.</p><p>As the couples attempt to win the hearts of each other – and the public – one couple will ultimately triumph and be crowned <i>Love Island</i> winners</p>","updated":1782724182,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/11363"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3650898","name":"Episode 28"},"nextepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3650899","name":"Episode 29"}}},"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3650900"},"show":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/11363","name":"Love Island"}}},{"id":3652847,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3652847/paramedics-on-scene-7x02-episode-2","name":"Episode 2","season":7,"number":2,"type":"regular","airdate":"2026-07-05","airtime":"21:00","airstamp":"2026-07-05T20:00:00+00:00","runtime":60,"rating":{"average":null},"image":null,"summary":"<p>Stevie and Pete of the the Special Operations Response Team rescue a man suffering a mental health crisis. In Dunoon, paramedic Ben treats a man who has a blood clot in his lungs.</p>","show":{"id":45263,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/45263/paramedics-on-scene","name":"Paramedics on Scene","type":"Documentary","language":"English","genres":["Medical"],"status":"Running","runtime":60,"averageRuntime":60,"premiered":"2019-09-29","ended":null,"officialSite":"https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/m00091s7","schedule":{"time":"21:00","days":["Sunday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":90,"network":{"id":1648,"name":"BBC Scotland","country":{"name":"United Kingdom","code":"GB","timezone":"Europe/London"},"officialSite":null},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":null,"thetvdb":370969,"imdb":"tt11383308"},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/630/1576079.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/630/1576079.jpg"},"summary":"<p>The Scottish Ambulance Service serves over five million people, from remote islands to busy cities.</p><p><b>Paramedics on Scene</b> captures the life-saving work of Scotland's paramedics as they respond to emergencies wherever they are needed.</p><p>Each episode features extraordinary stories from across the country, with the cameras following divisional ambulances responding to high-pressure 999 calls, 24 hours a day. The call-outs ranged from air-ambulances in Highlands and Islands, bringing treatment to Scotland's remotest communities to city centre car smashes to dealing onsite with life-threatening sepsis.</p>","updated":1782684030,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/45263"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3652846","name":"Episode 1"},"nextepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3652847","name":"Episode 2"}}},"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3652847"},"show":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/45263","name":"Paramedics on Scene"}}},{"id":3656749,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3656749/terror-on-long-island-1x01-episode-1","name":"Episode 1","season":1,"number":1,"type":"regular","airdate":"2026-07-05","airtime":"21:00","airstamp":"2026-07-05T20:00:00+00:00","runtime":60,"rating":{"average":null},"image":null,"summary":"<p>The series begins by plunging viewers into the early days of the investigation, starting with the mysterious disappearance of Shannan Gilbert in May 2010. Gilbert, a young escort, vanished after making a frantic 911 call from a remote area near Gilgo Beach. What began as a search for a missing woman quickly spiraled into something far more sinister when police uncovered the remains of four other women, all wrapped in burlap and discarded along the desolate stretch of Ocean Parkway.</p>","show":{"id":92828,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/92828/terror-on-long-island","name":"Terror on Long Island","type":"Documentary","language":"English","genres":[],"status":"In Development","runtime":60,"averageRuntime":60,"premiered":"2026-07-05","ended":null,"officialSite":"https://www.sphere-abacus.com/programme/4377/terror-on-long-island","schedule":{"time":"","days":["Sunday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":77,"network":{"id":1706,"name":"Sky Crime","country":{"name":"United Kingdom","code":"GB","timezone":"Europe/London"},"officialSite":null},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":null,"thetvdb":null,"imdb":null},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/630/1577193.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/630/1577193.jpg"},"summary":"<p><b>Terror on Long Island</b> takes viewers deep into the chilling saga of a string of murders that haunted the Long Island area for over a decade.</p><p>Throughout the series, viewers will be guided through the intricate details of the investigation, with exclusive access to first-hand testimonies from those directly involved in the case. Retired detectives, FBI agents, and forensic experts will provide insight into the challenges they faced, the breakthroughs that led to Heuermann's arrest, and the lingering questions that remain. The series also includes emotional interviews with the families of the victims, who share their experiences of loss, frustration, and the painful journey toward closure.</p>","updated":1783008194,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/92828"},"nextepisode":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3656749","name":"Episode 1"}}},"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/3656749"},"show":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/92828","name":"Terror on Long Island"}}},{"id":3650429,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/3650429/mock-the-week-summer-specials-1x05-episode-5","name":"Episode 5","season":1,"number":5,"type":"regular","airdate":"2026-07-05","airtime":"22:00","airstamp":"2026-07-05T21:00:00+00:00","runtime":60,"rating":{"average":null},"image":null,"summary":"<p>Highlights from the previous four weeks, plus some un-seen material.</p>","show":{"id":92454,"url":"https://www.tvmaze.com/shows/92454/mock-the-week-summer-specials","name":"Mock the Week: Summer Specials","type":"Panel Show","language":"English","genres":["Comedy"],"status":"Running","runtime":60,"averageRuntime":60,"premiered":"2026-06-07","ended":null,"officialSite":"https://www.discoveryplus.com/gb/en/shows/mock-the-week-summer-specials/4e7f7c1e-64f1-4151-a9bb-f1a9831aeea8","schedule":{"time":"21:00","days":["Sunday"]},"rating":{"average":null},"weight":93,"network":{"id":645,"name":"TLC","country":{"name":"United Kingdom","code":"GB","timezone":"Europe/London"},"officialSite":null},"webChannel":null,"dvdCountry":null,"externals":{"tvrage":null,"thetvdb":null,"imdb":null},"image":{"medium":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/628/1571332.jpg","original":"https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/628/1571332.jpg"},"summary":"<p>Dara Ó Briain is back with a summer run of topical chat and hilarious games, featuring a host of top stand-up comedians.</p>","updated":1782846806,"_links":{"self":{"href":"https://api.tvmaze.com/shows/92454"},"previousepisode":{"href":"https://ap